parameters:
The heart calms down in the flickering of flames.... \! The
party's health has been fully restored!
\SE[2]Oh... I didn't know there was a place like this.

\SE[12]For now, let's regroup here and send a request for
reinforcements to Yurisine... \!\SE[13]After that, we'll launch a
direct assault on the enemy's main base...!\!\SE[15] That's the
plan!

\SE[4]How are we going to communicate with the reinforcements?
\SE[3]It's quite far and the path is hidden.
\SE[1]Thank you for asking! There is a preparation for this...!

\SE[14]This is the Auto Boat-kun that I stayed up all night to
make! \SE[10]He will serve as our Messenger!

\SE[16]Alright! It's time to set off on our journey! \SE[10]The
time has come for each of us to fulfill our roles...!

\SE[11]You thought we were going straight...!? \SE[15]No, we're
actually going to use the opening and closing of the floodgate to
divert the flow over there!

\SE[76]Well... so this is going according to plan? \.In that
case, shall we take a little break? \!\SE[3]The real thing starts
from now on, after all.
